  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures or ALICANTE - charts 19-1, 19-2 and 19-3 from Jeppesen GSPRM 2017.<i> </i><br>An aircraft is flying VFR along the coastline, approaching Alicante Aerodrome (LEAL) from the southwest with plans to enter via the South Route and land at the airport. What is the latest point at which two-way radio contact with Alicante Tower must be established?</p>",
  "options": {
    "a": "Overhead ALT VOR.",
    "b": "<p>At reporting point SE.</p>",
    "c": "<p>At reporting point SW.</p>",
    "d": "When crossing the ATZ boundary."
  },
  "correctOption": "c",
